Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 到处乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个机体是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅凭一架机体就具有匹敌联结机的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是联结机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的 连同伴机都没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样的话 噪音介入系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被强制解除联结的原因就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我没有确凿的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 不能使用联结机的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就没有胜算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真由 帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢恬不知耻的出现啊 我要为比森报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 塔基姆 听听雏怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪奥 联结
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和他打只有这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是艾维拉小姐说有电波干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没有试 怎么知道不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接 迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不知道这是白费力气吗 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 他的行动突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚 但这是机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 看来到极限时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上重新启动 不要设定极限时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不这么做的话 对大脑的影响…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要借口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是一点都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使系统是一流的 如果部件是二流的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就无法完全发挥机能的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名为驾驶员的这个部件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了 渡濑青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那种事可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是现在这种座舱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要追加系统 理论上是可能的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却跟走钢丝一般危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这就可以解释发生电波干扰的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前给你看过的计划 说不定可以实现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能追加上系统的时间是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也没有其他选项了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的战斗是正义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统的构筑完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时机由我们这边指示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副长也问了同样的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你看 公主殿下来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是雏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 掩护那女孩是舰长的指示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个一个都让我这么火大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你又要说试试看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不是很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别搞砸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:07:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里乖乖待着 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了青叶之后 我会好好和你玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独立模式 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接 LUXON
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在联结机的系统内制造虚拟人格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过与其建立假想连接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令单独联结成为可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在如此短的时间里构筑出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是匆忙赶制的 和本来的使用方式也不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对驾驶员的负担也会很重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能使用很短的一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但联结是为了同调两个驾驶员的思考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将思考数据以素粒子等级 传送至1纳秒后的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单独的联结 因为是和自身进行联结
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要接受信息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 多余的传送数据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从传送数据被接受来看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介入联结系统的噪音 那就是电波干扰的正体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算构筑了系统 机体性能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能放出同样的噪音 就能抵消电波干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独立模式 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接 青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能不如艾维拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 只要我有部件的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优秀的部件！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人进行联结？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶君和雏·里亚赞的emphatier波形惊人的一致
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这在系统上 也可以被认定为同一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以让迪奥进行联结的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还是未知领域 不做做看的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被吞没了 我的思考数据…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏的记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的联结实验 只有雏一个人穿越了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初在联合…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那个循环…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比森 是你吧 坐在那个上面的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你们全杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾弗格尼·克达尔 立刻停止战斗行为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将对阁下以国家内乱罪予以逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以暴力夺取的政权毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对行政局的残暴抱持不满的同志非常多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着你上宇宙的期间 事情比想象中进展的还快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击阿拉斯加基地做的太过火了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个被害影像成为了导火索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己给自己挖了坟墓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原临时最高会议议长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面向全军播放了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说得救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个战场由我来支配
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我来支配
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的复仇还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持续了70年的 我的复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手吧 比森
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就这样捏碎你吧 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你乖乖躺在我下面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心情我有一点明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直看着雏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡濑青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而你想要保护的东西 是自尊和自我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我 我们也有想要保护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我要毁灭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方攻击卫星出现高热能反应 现在仍在增大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把卫星上储存的3年份的NECTORIBIUM一口气解放
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种分量的能量 这颗卫星也不可能承受得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑 我可不是可以死在这种地方的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的头脑 我的研究怎么能在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没法破坏卫星也没关系 只要能错开射线就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nectar屏障？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人攻击目标计算出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐基利亚共和国 甘多 木伦陶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联合加盟国 澳大利亚的加尔哥尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三…三个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为什么连自己的国家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是所有世界上为数不多的NECTORIBIUM出产地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是对据说有数十年份的NECTORIBIUM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用巨大nectar炮击中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会引发大规模的诱爆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:17:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会毁灭…吧 地球它…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让那种事发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们直接把它打掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 到卫星的距离…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联结机的话说不定赶得上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不试试可不知道 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经赶不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个 停止那个才是首先要干的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾薇拉小姐 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶他们跳跃了时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联结系统 为了不让思考出现时滞进行同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以素粒子等级 将信号传递到1纳秒后的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们的思考同步到不需要的程度的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把信号从0秒传递到0秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为了补完传递到1纳秒后的未来这个现象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把接受者和接收机送往1纳秒前的过去？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事是真的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道啊 但是只有这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如说那是真的 青叶他们为了回过去1纳秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跳100万次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移动距离继续增大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊 青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐标 E7—R1出现特异点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去 迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会被吸进去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BRADYON已经到极限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要追的话 我们去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 弗洛姆 迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪奥 你也看到了 所以应该知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要这样回到过去的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 做梦也没有想到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到能在70年后的未来 交到挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我向大家问好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说我一直以来受大家关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想说的话 自己去说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已经没有那个时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:21:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 突然出现 把我们搞得很混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦 迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LUXON NEXT以及KARURA 信号消失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点就赶不上下一堂课了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.88,0:23:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在哪里见过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 雏 这是在搭讪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我们是第一次见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.23,0:23:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫渡濑青叶 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓…弓原雏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:49.23,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,心で呼ぶ　惹かれあう彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:49.23,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,心的呼应 响应的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:57.88,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,痛みの理由(わけ)も忘れて　今だけどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:57.88,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,痛的理由 请暂且忘记 我在此深深祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:22:07.08,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,キミを知っている　キミを探しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:22:07.08,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,我深知你 我在一直寻找着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:15.80,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,引き止められない光の残像に　そっとくちづけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:15.80,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,轻轻吻向那已飘渺的光的残像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:24.81,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,躊躇いが僅かな　希望への糸口なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:24.81,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40}你那稍稍的犹豫不决 成为了那连接希望的蛛丝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:33.52,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,彷徨った数だけ　優しい朝へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:33.52,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40}你那微微的彷徨 拉近了与那温柔黎明的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:42.56,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,あの空に還る未来で　救いたい　守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:42.56,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40}想去拯救 想去保护 那早已归还于天空的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:49.44,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,その夢に届く未来で　待っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:49.44,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,请留步 那已经早已传达过梦想的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:58.86,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと出会える愛に　手を伸ばして欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:58.86,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能与我一起去抓住 那注定相遇的爱
